    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's more than just a burden. it's like i'm performing a role in a play that's already been canceled. i have to wake up, walk, talk, pretend i'm still part of the world when i know the foundation is gone. it's exhausting to keep the mask up when there's nothing behind it. i just wonder if it would be more honest to just... stop performing. to just let the performance end for good.",
